Bases: object

static alpha(graph, xmin=None) → float[source]¶

Find the alpha of the power law of a Graph Object (the coefficient used to assume a graph follows a Scale.Free Topology) :param float xmin: at what “x” on the degree distribution the power law will be fitted :return: a float representing the fitted power low distribution of the graph
